*xca-0.9.3-r1 (22 Mar 2013)

  22 Mar 2013; Alon Bar-Lev <alonbl@gentoo.org> +xca-0.9.3-r1.ebuild:
  Change dev-libs/openssl[-bindist] to dev-libs/openssl[bindist=], as xca
  detects automatically if openssl supports ec or not, while not having explicit
  way to enable/disable. bug#462510, thanks to wmatusiak

  02 Mar 2013; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> xca-0.9.0.ebuild,
  xca-0.9.1.ebuild, xca-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Move Qt dependencies to the new category

